      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Roll the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice!) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1617029377436-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1617029377436-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
